                <![CDATA[<p>平治近日在香港推出針對全線 EQ 系列電動車的全新 Mobile Service 流動售後服務，車主可在自行選擇的地點安排維修服務，節省往返維修中心時間，提升日程便利性，體驗真正的「Service at your convenience」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1240996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_133404-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_133404-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_133404-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲流動售後服務車</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1240987" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121648-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121648-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121648-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1240986" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121644-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121644-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121644-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1240990" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121904-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121904-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121904-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style=