5-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_135725-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1241005" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_135808-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_135808-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_135808-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1241006" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_140217-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_140217-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_140217-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1241008" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_140830-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_140830-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_140830-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1241010" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_141633-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_141633-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_141633-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>香港成為平治於歐洲以外首個推行流動服務的市場，領先亞太