            <title>【COMPUTEX 2024】MSI AI CoPilot+ PC 系列，搭載 Intel Core Ultra / AMD Ryzen AI 300 處理器</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/msi-copilotpc/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=msi-copilotpc</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/msi-copilotpc/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 12:00:15 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSI Prestige 13 AI+ Evo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSI Prestige 14 AI+ Evo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSI Prestige 16 AI+ Evo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSI Prestige A16 AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSI Summit 13 AI+ Evo]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1240760</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">一年一度的 Computex 台北國際電腦展引來不少大廠推出新機，MSI 宣佈推多款新 AI CoPilot+PC，專為遊戲及內容創作而設計，搭載最新 Intel Core Ultra 及 AMD Ryzen AI 300 系列處理器，新處理器更節能，使手提電腦擁有更長電池續航力和更薄機身。MSI 推出的新 AI 手提電腦有多款搭載 AMD Ryzen AI 300 系列處理器。處理器採用新架構 XDNA 2，架構性能比前代產品提升達三倍。在手提電腦上可以直接運行生成式 AI 或大型語言模型。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1240761 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-5-694x475.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="475" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-5-694x475.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲MSI 宣佈推多款新 AI CoPilot+PC</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>MSI Prestige A16 AI</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">MSI Prestige A16 AI 手提電腦與 MSI Summit A16 AI+ 硬件相近，配備 AMD Ryzen AI 9 365 處理器、32GB RAM（最高）及 AMD Radeon 顯示卡，儲存空間最高達 2TB SSD。然而，Prestige 更輕，重量僅 4.18 磅。其他功能包括白色背光鍵盤帶 Copilot 鍵、82Wh 電池。</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>MSI Prestige 14 AI+ Evo</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">MSI Prestige 14 AI+ Evo 配備 Intel Core Ultra 處理器，32GB RAM（最高），14 吋 2880×1800 OLED 顯示器，16:10 屏佔比，更加方便瀏覽網頁。與其他 Prestige 機款一樣，MSI Prestige 14 AI+ Evo 也配有白色背光鍵盤及 Wi-Fi 7 。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1240763 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240604_122640-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240604_122640-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240604_122640-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MSI Prestige A16 AI 配備 AMD Ryzen AI 9 365 處理器，MSI Prestige 14 AI+ Evo 配備 Intel Core Ultra 處理器</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/20/msi-claw-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】MSI Claw　外形　手感　效能　打機體驗　散熱　屏幕 5 大優點 + 缺點開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/msi-summit-e13-ai-evo-ai/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【COMPUTEX 2024】MSI Summit E13 AI Evo AI 登場，搭載 Intel Core Ultra 7 處理器 155H</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/05/msi-lunar-lake-prestige-ai-pc/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【Computex 2024】MSI 發佈一系列 AI PC　同場加映 18 吋 Mercedes-AMG 聯乘筆電</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>MSI Prestige 16 AI+ Evo</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">MSI Prestige 16 AI+ Evo 配備 Intel Core Ultra 處理器、32GB RAM（最高）及 16 吋 OLED 顯示器，支援 100% DCI-P3 色域，適合不同創作者。Prestige 16 AI+ Evo 重 3.30 磅，配有 Wi-Fi 7、99.9Wh 大電池、白色背光鍵盤及 1.7mm 的鍵程。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1240767 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-8-694x451.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="451" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-8-694x451.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲MSI Prestige 16 AI+ Evo 配備 Intel Core Ultra 處理器</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>MSI Prestige 13 AI+ Evo</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">MSI Prestige 13 AI+ Evo 是 Prestige 系列中螢幕最小的機款，但也是最輕的，只重 2.20 磅。搭載 Intel Core Ultra 處理器，13.3 吋 2880×1800 OLED 顯示器，75Wh 電池，Wi-Fi 7 及兩個 Thunderbolt 4 連接埠及白色背光鍵盤帶 Copilot 鍵。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1240765 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-7-694x476.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="476" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-7-694x476.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-7.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MSI Prestige 13 AI+ Evo 是 Prestige 系列中螢幕最小的機款，搭載 Intel Core Ultra 處理器</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>MSI Summit 13 AI+ Evo</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">MSI Summit 13 AI+ Evo 配備 Intel Core Ultra 處理器，最高 32GB RAM 及 2TB SSD 儲存空間，足以應付辦公、照片編輯及日常活動。13.3 吋顯示器，16:10 屏佔比，支援 100% sRGB 色域，色彩表現出色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1240764 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-6-694x469.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-6-694x469.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MSI Summit 13 AI+ Evo 配備 Intel Core Ultra 處理器</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/20/msi-claw-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】MSI Claw　外形　手感　效能　打機體驗　散熱　屏幕 5 大優點 + 缺點開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/msi-summit-e13-ai-evo-ai/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【COMPUTEX 2024】MSI Summit E13 AI Evo AI 登場，搭載 Intel Core Ultra 7 處理器 155H</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/05/msi-lunar-lake-prestige-ai-pc/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【Computex 2024】MSI 發佈一系列 AI PC　同場加映 18 吋 Mercedes-AMG 聯乘筆電</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/msi-copilotpc/notebook/">【COMPUTEX 2024】MSI AI CoPilot+ PC 系列，搭載 Intel Core Ultra / AMD Ryzen AI 300 處理器</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
